import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { handleSuccess } from '../utils' import CalendarView from './CalendarView' import './Home.css' const Home = () => { const navigate = useNavigate() const [loggedInUser, setLoggedInUser] = useState('') const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ professor: '', department: '', school: '', room: '', day: '', startTime: '', endTime: '' }) const [bookings, setBookings] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { setLoggedInUser(localStorage.getItem('handleLogout')) }, []) const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.removeItem('token') localStorage.removeItem('handleLogout') handleSuccess('User Logged Out') setTimeout(() => navigate('/login'), 1000) } const handleChange = (e) => { setFormData({ ...formData, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }) } const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault() setBookings([...bookings, formData]) setFormData({ professor: '', department: '', school: '', room: '', day: '', startTime: '', endTime: '' }) } return ( <> {/* NAVBAR */}
Conference Room Booking System
Welcome {loggedInUser}
{/* MAIN CONTENT */}
{/* LEFT: BOOKING FORM */}

Book a Conference Room

{/* RIGHT: CALENDAR */}

Weekly Schedule

) } export default Home
